{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 175990, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 31377, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就是整天凑薄膜配方，测量子霍尔", "timestamp": 1595749563, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 175996, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 31377, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谁说凝聚态只有实验的……", "timestamp": 1595749762, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 175997, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 31377, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就没有做理论和计算的过来澄清一下吗……", "timestamp": 1595749783, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 176076, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 31377, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "凝聚态包括理论实验和计算三个部分，其中和应用最接轨也（相对来说）更好发文章的做法就是在实验\\计算上往具体材料上靠拢，但有研究品位的物理学家一般不会（只）干这些事情，比如物理系的xqk，wyy两位实验大佬目前主攻高温超导，这样的研究和材料有关，但也包含了对物理原理的探索，远远超出了“排列组合”的范畴", "timestamp": 1595751897, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 176084, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 31377, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "另外“凝聚态”其实范围很广，广义上研究量子多体系统都会把自己称为“凝聚态”", "timestamp": 1595751962, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 31377, "reply": 5, "tag": null, "text": "#31321\n凝聚态是半个材料？？打算大三seminar做凝聚态的人凌乱了，真的吗？？", "timestamp": 1595748564, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782596, "url": "", "vote": {}}}